110
00:10:35,791 --> 00:10:37,416
- Cakaplah.
- Okey.

111
00:10:38,208 --> 00:10:40,875
- Misalnya, cara nak keluarkan emas.
- Kersik.

112
00:10:40,958 --> 00:10:44,875
Kita akan lebur 90 tan emas
menjadi butir-butir beras.

113
00:10:44,958 --> 00:10:47,666
Kemudian, perejangan jet.

114
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:51,000
Kita akan keluarkannya
menggunakan pam tekanan.

115
00:10:51,083 --> 00:10:52,500
- Guna pam?
- Ya.

116
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,083
Melalui paip?

117
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:57,333
Ada pam tekanan di Bank Sepanyol?

118
00:10:57,416 --> 00:10:58,500
- Tiada.
- Jadi?

119
00:10:58,583 --> 00:11:02,500
Kami terpaksa curinya
dari pelantar minyak di Norway.

120
00:11:02,583 --> 00:11:03,875
Apa pendapat awak?

121
00:11:05,125 --> 00:11:08,541
Ada sebuah di Arab Saudi,
tapi saya malas nak pergi sejauh itu.

122
00:11:08,625 --> 00:11:09,583
Saya faham.

123
00:11:09,666 --> 00:11:10,791
Paling penting,

124
00:11:10,875 --> 00:11:15,208
pancutan air panas berwarna keemasan
akan mengalir melalui paip itu.

125
00:11:15,291 --> 00:11:16,791
Rancangan ini sempurna.

126
00:11:17,291 --> 00:11:20,416
Andres, rancangan ini
ialah satu kesilapan besar.

127
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:23,625
Berapa usia paip itu? 50 tahun? 70 tahun?

128
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:29,291
Seratus tahun.

129
00:11:29,375 --> 00:11:33,291
Awak rasa ia mampu menampung
tekanan aliran emas yang tinggi?

130
00:11:33,375 --> 00:11:34,250
Ia takkan pecah!

131
00:11:36,166 --> 00:11:38,750
