tapi pilih yang kasual saja.

222
00:16:42,958 --> 00:16:46,083
<i>Palermo dan Berlin sependapat</i>
<i>tentang erti kematangan</i>

223
00:16:46,166 --> 00:16:48,291
<i>iaitu pengakhiran angan-angan</i>

224
00:16:48,375 --> 00:16:51,625
<i>dan permulaan hidup</i>
<i>yang disulami kepahitan realiti.</i>

225
00:16:52,125 --> 00:16:56,750
<i>Menjadi matang sama seperti menua.</i>
<i>Perlahan-lahan, ia menguburkan impian.</i>

226
00:17:05,665 --> 00:17:07,165
Bogota, selam!

227
00:17:09,083 --> 00:17:10,458
- Bogota!
- Apa?

228
